<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Plasmospace</title>
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="img/logo.svg" type="image/x-icon">
    </head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="js/tailwind.js"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        'ps-yellow': '#fdbf44',
                        'ps-red': '#e64b2f'
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <body class="bg-white text-black overflow-x-hidden">
        <header class="shadow-lg  z-10 sticky top-0 left-0 bg-white w-full">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-5 py-5 flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer gap-3">
                <img src="img/logo.svg" alt="" class="h-10 md:h-12">
                <img src="img/workmark.svg" alt="Plasmospace" class="h-10 md:h-12">
            </div>
        </header>
        <main class="bg-yellow-200 relative">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-5 pb-20 lg:py-48 flex items-center justify-between gap-24 flex-col lg:flex-row">
                <img src="img/mockup.png" class="lg:absolute top-0 right-0 opacity-0">
                <img src="img/mockup.png" class="absolute top-0 right-0 ">
                <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex lg:items-start items-center justify-center gap-8 flex-col">
                    <h1 class="font-black text-5xl lg:text-7xl text-center lg:text-left text-red-700">
                        <span class="text-black">Find</span>
                        plasma donors
                        <span class="text-black">
                            in your city.</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl">Plasmospace helps connect donors and recipients with a click of a button.</p>
                    <a href="#">
                        <img src="img/play-store.png" alt="Download from Play Store" class="h-12">
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <section class="bg-yellow-100">
            <div class="mx-auto container px-5 py-20 space-y-5">
                <h2 class="uppercase text-center pb-10 font-black text-5xl text-red-700">
                    Features
                    <span class="text-black">Offered</span>
                </h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-5 gap-10">
                    {% for feature in features %}
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-yellow-200 p-5 rounded-md shadow-lg">
                            <i class="{{ feature.classes }} text-5xl text-red-700"></i>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-center mt-10">{{ feature.name }}</h3>
                            <p>{{ feature.desc }}</p>
                        </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="bg-yellow-100">
            <div class="mx-auto container px-5 py-20 space-y-5">
                <h2 class="uppercase text-center pb-10 font-black text-5xl text-red-700">
                    <span class="text-black">About</span>
                    Plasmospace
                </h2>
                <ul class="space-y-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto list-disc">
                    <li>
                        Plasma Donation system, aims at providing an adequate supply of plasma transfusion and donation centers and hospitals.
                        Plasma is necessary for several treatments and surgeries like cancer, hemophilia, transplant surgery, etc and it's still
                        a limited resource. Plasma donation will play a fundamental role in health care systems, aiming at guaranteeing an
                        adequate plasma availability to meet the demand and save lives.
                    </li>
                    <li>For plasma donation the person has to be at least 18 years of age or older and should be at least 50 kilograms. The
                        person will also have to get a physical examination and get tested for viruses. Donating plasma is different from
                        donating blood. When donating blood, it goes straight to the collection of the bag and then later is separated in the
                        lab and while donating plasma the blood drawn goes to a machine where all the contents of blood are separated.</li>
                    <li>
                        Plasma can be donated every four weeks. Automated donation allows collection of a larger amount of plasma from one donor
                        at one sitting the whole donation of blood. This is good for donors of type AB since they are universal donors. Plasma
                        requires precaution of collection and storage. Its shelf life is limited from donation to utilization i.e. 1 year and
                        after it's thawed it lasts for about 24 hours to 5 days depending on the product. Hence a plasma donation system is
                        needed, a supply block chain should meet the daily demand of plasma and follow its temporal pattern.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Plasma donation and the related management problems can be classified into: Donorâ€™s registration, plasma collection,
                        plasma screening/evaluation, inventory storage and delivery. It concerns the strategic decisions which are the location
                        of the healthcare center and tactical operation systems like production of multiple products, plasma allocation health
                        care centers and hospitals, control of the inventory levels and delivery.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="bg-yellow-100">
            <div class="mx-auto container px-5 py-20 space-y-5">
                <h2 class="uppercase text-center pb-10 font-black text-5xl text-red-700">
                    <span class="text-black">The</span>
                    team
                </h2>
                <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-5 gap-10 items-center justify-center justify-items-center">
                    {% for member in members %}
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-yellow-200 p-5 rounded-md w-fit shadow-lg">
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-center">
                                    <span class="text-red-700">{{ member.fname }}</span>
                                    {{ member.lname }}</h3>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-lg font-semibold">{{ member.roll }}</span>
                            <a href="tel:91{{ member.phone }}">
                                <i class="fas fa-phone mr-1"></i>
                                <span class="underline">{{ member.phone }}</span>
                            </a>
                            <a href="mailto:{{ member.email }}" class=" hidden md:inline">
                                <i class="fas fa-envelope mr-1"></i>
                                <span class="underline">{{ member.email }}</span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="bg-red-800 text-yellow-50">
            <div class="mx-auto container px-5 py-10 flex flex-col items-center">
                <h2 class=" font-bold text-3xl text-center pb-4">Donate and receive plasma now!</h2>
                <a href="#">
                    <img src="img/play-store.png" alt="Download from Play Store" class="h-12">
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <footer>
            <div class="mx-auto container px-5 py-2 flex justify-center">
                <span class="font-bold">
                    &copy; 2022 - Plasmospace
                </span>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>